{
  "name": "WF1 — Follow-Up Reminder (Day Before)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 1: Follow-Up Reminder\n\n**Trigger:** Daily at 9:00 AM\n\n**Logic:** Finds all patients whose `follow_up_date` is tomorrow, `status = pending`, and `message_count < 5`. Sends a WhatsApp reminder, updates the patient record, and logs the send.\n\n**Before activating:**\n1. Set credential on \"Read Patients\" node → Google Sheets account\n2. Set credential on \"Send WhatsApp Reminder\" node → Twilio Basic Auth\n3. Set credential on \"Update Patient Record\" node → Google Sheets account\n4. Set credential on \"Log to Message_Logs\" node → Google Sheets account",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 9 * * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-000000000002",
      "name": "Daily 9AM Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [240, 380]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "read",
        "documentId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "={{ $env.GOOGLE_SHEETS_ID }}",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "sheetName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "Patients",
          "mode": "name"
        },
        "filtersUI": {},
        "options": {}
